「第五课」捕捉动物的灵动：用好布局，你画的大闸蟹能从纸上跑出来

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app2gglt1bm4926/v_5c04b45b25b37_DATTJKZJ

<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: -14px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(145, 197, 235); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: -14px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 100%; float: right; background-color: rgb(145, 197, 235); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: -12px 0px 0px; padding: 18px 10px 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(145, 197, 235); border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 524px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px 5px; background-color: rgb(145, 197, 235); color: rgb(247, 247, 247); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">什么人适合来学习？</strong></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 2px dotted rgb(146, 198, 236); width: 145px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">• 只要喜欢「国画小品」这种绘画风格，无论什么人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">• 一次毛笔都没摸过、一张画都没画过的人，也没问题</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">• 小朋友喜欢，也是适合来学习的哦~</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 524px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">•&nbsp;课程订阅后不支持退款。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/76241800_1539921943.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiazozsnquwiaf7slxrpya6dpx4j71n7x8ndeicnfwzga2w3bgltq6tt5ng/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/31356000_1539921989.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshnhvvynlgqwwgx3sjbglhzawibjdsaig9ymaia8w6m59hftcralswkfk9weicsyflocrazdf4asrsmuhq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(133, 121, 126); letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;">文 | 王小麦</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“某音”刚火的时候，我和闺蜜纷纷入坑。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">睡前刷一会儿，醒来刷一会儿，厕所时刷一会儿，尬聊时刷一会儿。无聊了还会录上一段，取乐自己，愉悦他人。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">很快我们就觉得，这东西堪比“吸毒”：沉浸其中赛神仙，清醒时恨不得抽自己两耳光——又在浪费生命！于是，我们又纷纷戒毒。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不久前见闺蜜，她“复吸”了。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">闺蜜说，自己也知道应该多读书、多看报，但每个累成狗的下班时刻，总想留点“不动脑”的时间给自己。除了体力运动之外，她实在不知道还能干点什么。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">原来，无聊这件事，我们在升级了精神追求之后，竟然也面临着“无处安放”的窘境。&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/62647700_1539921989.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiazqn9i6botpftg9bm68srqumghpqi23o02wfmdp0gqbkziayp12wwakq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">想起小时候，没手机、没电脑、没iPad，但我们会唱歌、会跳舞、会画画。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">虽然算不上什么特长，但也从不吝啬向大人们“秀”出来，也对收获的或真诚、或敷衍的表扬，无比自豪！&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">没有哪个孩子会担忧“无聊”来袭，他们很会在“无脑”的世界里，活出奇迹般的充实。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">而我们这些成年人，如此用脑的生活，却过得这么干瘪。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“不如画画吧！”&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">打着心疼闺蜜的旗号，我灵光一闪后，简直是在对自己呐喊。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“唱歌跳舞什么的，这把年纪搞这些还是有点门槛的，但画画，拿起笔就可以做到呀！”&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/12816900_1539921990.cn/mmbiz_gif/uliackyshnhvvynlgqwwgx3sjbglhzawya8x2zeq08ikxqo97iaibm2wiavibpabyuhjjugf0nqw48oqkl2dsiawr7w/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">△&nbsp;杨立一随身画册</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">小时候学画画，爸妈说不求你当艺术家，这能锻炼你对自然的观察、对世界的表达。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那时候叛逆，总想怼一句：“那你们怎么不学？”&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">当我们到了爸妈的年纪，想起小时候的发问，也想问问自己：“对呀！我自己怎么不学？”&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">对呀，长大了的我们，真不如小时候的你自己。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">和自然的亲近、眼睛观察的灵气、对色彩的想象力，在不断精进的领导力、时间管理、社交技法中，逐渐退化得无影无踪。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那种记录在人类基因里的，用画画说话的本能，被我们生生蹂躏成“没什么用处”的不务正业。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">既然“现实”惯了，我索性对“画画”这件本身就“好感力”爆棚的娱乐活动，做了一番理性的思考：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">画画对于实用主义的我们，到底有什么用？&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.2; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span style="margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.6; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 1; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1、能给元气“充电”&nbsp;</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">科学实验表明，人们把注意力集中在“感知当下”的时候，大脑前额区和中心区的Alpha波会明显增加，Alpha波是人们学习与思考的最佳脑波状态。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这个状态下，我们身体是放松的，能量消耗很少，脑部获得的能量较高，会产生一种清晰、愉快的感受。&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">画画的过程，使用的是“形象思维”，相比我们总是用到的“逻辑思维”来说，是一种没时间放飞意识、看到什么就是什么的“感知当下”的过程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">所以在画画的时候，人们很容易让自己松弛下来。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">说白了，就是画画可以从生理上，让你的身体实现“自供暖”，让你的元气得以充满能量。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/42656100_1539921990.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiay4cwysqueiazgv77gf7mapyib5k9cc0dc6fav7uphhmxdtpulajbsmga/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">△&nbsp;杨立一往期授课作品</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.2; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span style="margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.6; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 1; background-color: rgb(146, 198, 236); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2、发泄情绪</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">人类发明文字之前，就是用画画记事的，所以画画是最基础的“说话”。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">平时我们遇到情绪问题的时候，自己是无法清晰的意识到、并且还能准确地表达出来的。所以，找人倾诉这件事，有时候简直就是雪上加霜！抒情了大半天，落得个没人懂你的下场。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">画画，此刻就显得特别的暖心，它好像在拥抱着你，拍着你的背，轻轻的说：“语言说不清楚，那就画吧。不论画了个什么，发泄出来就好。”&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">突然发现还有很多好处：有品位、有谈资、有文化。这里就不多赘述了。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/67907100_1539921990.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiaeqxfwoj1c73goundxzvtggfkwm02tqicu9yfnxkdumj1gyv7icxsrgoq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">△&nbsp;杨立一往期授课作品</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">「虚度美学课堂」</strong></span>和<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">「云手艺课堂」</strong></span>在开发美学课程的时候，想到这里，突然觉得使命感来袭：&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">孩子们尚且有适合自己年纪的画画班，成年人的日常，也需要被认认真真的呵护。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">于是，便有了杨立一老师的《国画小品零基础入门课 | 一学就能“晒”的生活记录法》。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/96364800_1539921990.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshnhvvynlgqwwgx3sjbglhzawjsiacpuuetpt8z7slwgvbb1icjpud8w5ibsa0xzlzvcq8uj1craqyt0cw/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">提到“国画”这两个字，虚度君的本能反应就是：&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不行不行，太难了！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不行不行，太土了！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不行不行，太虚了！&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">当我们看了杨老师的课件后，突然就变了脸：&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">哎？这个好！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">哎？这个我想学！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">哎？那个我也喜欢！&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▽ 让虚度君“打脸”的国画小品，</span></span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box;">也是课程内容&nbsp;</span></strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/25762400_1539921991.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiae0nn9s3mgmregzwgujg0b0bhslwedmq0icieh4g4eb5la5o1mlw7t9a/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/53731200_1539921991.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiaickpliaxyb7jqbrsx7xo4dmhj7vekybsfva6df22b96z4natmpmkxfcq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/76909200_1539921991.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgiahatryxduicabzbn1w0miaeyfhiagqeyztogibesskxzzjvlibhg0unhbaa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 491.391px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">难吗？</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: auto; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section><section style="margin: -10px auto 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">虚度君：毕竟是老祖宗传下来的，我总觉得“国画”的难，不是“上青天”这么简单。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">杨立一：</strong>国画学好是挺难的，但是入门的门槛很低，有点像太极拳。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我们不需要把它供在神坛上，国画并没有什么日常、正式的分别，画到纸上都是心之所向。有一颗平常心，有想要表达的欲望，谁都可以画国画。&nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 491.391px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">要基本功吗？</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: auto; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section><section style="margin: -10px auto 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">虚度君：想起小时候练习拿毛笔，手型不对都要面临老师“小教鞭”的伺候。现在圆珠笔都不太拿， 是不是得刻苦修炼基本功？&nbsp;<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">杨立一：</strong>其实相比“素描”，国画在造型上的要求并不高，这也是说它好入门的原因。既然是入门，那么画的爽比画得好，应该对你更重要才是。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">当然想要精进国画，那肯定是要刻苦练习的，做任何事情都是一样，要取决于你对自己的要求。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 491.391px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;“晒”得出手吗？</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: auto; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(152, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section><section style="margin: -10px auto 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top: 9px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 9px solid transparent !important; border-right: 9px solid transparent !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">虚度君：我想画出照片上那种效果，课程学完能画出来吗？&nbsp;<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">杨立一：</strong>能！</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/13870900_1539921992.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngrjokpmggaljeiqs2zcrgia9htelaufhaecdqf2euudmicoytviap7jdrntjcgr6mti2ratnezguida/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; width: 218.391px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/39548300_1539921992.cn/mmbiz_png/ykjwficiatraq8hkpxgqh7zqcq8msfnzfyipdfghuq1csfo0ufa8yzjyjknwsw8scyfmnruibyicwqbrmzl94wkg9a/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 218.391px; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">刚认识杨立一老师的时候，她研究生都还没毕业。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那时候她就带着一群对国学、绘画颇有自己心得的成人学生，每周作画，还时不时组织大家前往各大博物馆看画。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">因为杨老师主攻的是中国美术史论和山水方向，她在教技法的间歇，会讲大量的史论、画家段子，讲她自己的观点，大家都听得津津有味，觉得她的观点不偏颇、不教条，很生动也很现代。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">杨立一老师教画画，不仅青春、有趣，还会更看重教大家日常中的“观察”：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 546px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px; border-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); border-right-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“在东方语境下，观察是感知，是用心而非眼去看。学过画画的人，感知力是很强的。秋天飘落的一片树叶，树叶慢慢从绿变成了黄色，即便最后蜷缩成枯叶，都能感受到那种巨大的生命力的冲击。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">有心观察的人，看自己的周遭事物，那简直像窦文涛说的，‘世间一切皆好看’ 。”</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">如今，杨老师在杭州，已经举办个人画展《荷境》，作品《渔父图》曾参加《渠宜书屋师生展》巡展，作品《你懂真好》参加了《古情今意——上海师范大学美术学院教学展》巡展。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/60491100_1539921992.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshnhvvynlgqwwgx3sjbglhzawh8x7cgxvinialsmm6oj089lyqjinzv3dbibglxklse51gtzp2gkiysdg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/87022900_1539921992.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshnhvvynlgqwwgx3sjbglhzawkdtfjbrcsf2fhxwhwvftjhux2soutnbho2jicr4ktjapzpwavftgf1q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">△ 《荷静》展览</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 518.688px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 0px 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; 